      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence to residual tolerance below 1e-6 for all equations; round-off error analysis documented; floating-point arithmetic precision verified for hemolysis accumulation path.",
      "rationale": "Solver convergence was monitored but iterative residual tolerances were set at 1e-4 for the hemolysis scalar equation. Round-off error analysis was not performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
